1. Core Framework
Django Built-ins: Authentication, Database, Admin Panel.
Forms & Views: For handling submissions and rendering templates.

2. Article Submission & Viewing
Models: Article, Comment.
Forms: ArticleForm, CommentForm.
Tools: PyPDF2, docx, pdfminer for file parsing; messages, login_required for UX and access.

3. Plagiarism Checker
Model: PlagiarismCheck.
Tools: BeautifulSoup, requests, nltk for checks; FileResponse for report download.

4. News & Announcements
Models: News, Announcement.
Forms: Admin tools for managing updates.

5. AI Chatbot
Model: DistilBART (transformers).
Tools: JsonResponse, csrf_exempt for interaction.

6. Contact & Email (SMTP)
Tools: send_mail, settings for user notifications.

7. Auth & Users
Forms: SignupForm, LoginForm.
Tools: login, logout, user_passes_test for access control.

8. File Downloads
Tool: reportlab for generating dynamic PDF reports.
